most_relevant.description:
This was my first time dining at Evergreen Downtown and I was very pleased with our choice.

I have eaten at expensive Chinese restaurants in Richmond and Vancouver, Canada, but this place does well at a very reasonable cost. Good food is not cheap, and people usually expect Americanized portions and food with excess protein or filling, but here you get appropriate portions and correctly prepared food, not sacrificing quality for quantity’s sake.

The atmosphere was beautiful at the early afternoon hour and the wait staff eased our unfamiliarity to the restaurant with welcoming smiles and pleasant attitude (mind you we were not the most polite as we entered being overheated and managing a hungry child, but they were nice regardless and we calmed in the peaceful atmosphere). In the  area at night I imagine it would be a beautiful place to for a date or relaxing dinner with friends.

Portions were more than acceptable at a traditional Chinese establishment, and I attach a picture of our lamb to show how much was left after serving three. The flavors were fantastic, through our own fault we did not ask them to make it spicy (Due to looking like a normal American man I find that many restaurants will not make things spicy enough for my tastes, and I will ask next time for some more Sichuan peppercorn).

Finally the service was appropriate and timely, and refills were provided as needed.

Dumplings were very wonderful textbook flavor. Could not have been better, and the meat and tofu were fresh and perfect for our tastes.

Price was fine, and tip was not required though it was deserved.

Thank you for a wonderful experience, and as I will be traveling to Ann Arbor with frequency this fall I am sure to return, as time and presence allow.

A wonderful birthday meal experience! A nice variety of vegetarian options. Rice is included with meal. Would highly recommend the Ginger and Garlic Eggplant! We both got drinks and still found the total to be reasonable! Great atmosphere, would recommend for any occasion!
REALLY excellent food! Very flavorful. Good portion sizes. Lots of great options, many of which are not the usual version of American Chinese food. Wish we lived nearby because I'd be a regular.

we had a wonderful experience dining at Evergreen tonight for the first time. The ginger garlic chicken is probably the best thing on the menu as of April 2024. The flavors are pronounced, but not too overwhelming… Simply delectable! And if you have special dietary needs they can make anything on the menu with low- or no-sodium, and spice levels can be customized as well.

Stopped in for lunch on a Saturday before a night game at the big house. First time here and couldn’t be more pleased. Atmosphere, staff, food were as good as one could hope for. Cumin Lamb was unbelievable, everything we ordered was perfect! Give it a try you won’t be disappointed!
I was not expecting this much good food and service, well done guys.. definitely will visit again.. beef stew with potatoes and fried rice very good, also the hot and sour soup..

What an awesome find! We've driven by a few times, but finally made the time to stop for our anniversary dinner. It is a clean, airy environment, with attentive waitstaff and incredibly fresh food. Once seated, we had time to browse through their electronic menu. It was nice to be able to tap menu dishes to find out what ingredients they used. I was able to order a vegetable dish without sauce (it's sad, I know, but it works for my dietary recreations). The wanton soup was amazing. My husband enjoyed a fried rice dish. And my vegetable dish was fresh and cooked well. While the dining area was quiet while we were there for an early dinner, there were numerous take out orders being picked up. Everything was organized and efficient. We would recommend.

Absolutely love the comfortable, chill-like setting and atmosphere!

The waiters are friendly, and check on you if everything is alright.

Ordered a bowl of Lo Mein with shrimps. Not gonna lie, the portion is quite decent and fill me up instantly. Will definitely visit again with some friends, or even dates!
